Class RawDataProvider

Direct Known Subclasses:
PlotDataProvider
public class RawDataProvider
extends Channel

Class for trace representation, holds raw trace data and introduces an abstract way to get it. Trace data here is list of Segments.

Author:
Max Kokoulin
